{"tid":339833,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻狗今日過左身","createTime":"2017-07-29T11:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T18:37:47.000Z","uid":1870,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31354f72b4865674556cbc79d4aef3c8069d3a65","tid":339833,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"養左8年，細個讀書陪到我長大成人，心情仲低落過失戀果陣，忍唔住喊左出黎，有冇過來人分享下當時既心路歷程"},{"pid":"c639c51b4d2c5484bf363dc05e13c38a07958585","tid":339833,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537872f16b9a4795482f8fc7657bb8adb4c984ec","tid":339833,"uid":55593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cbf0fbc1f1c2817680c126ef5030622a2886c7","tid":339833,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"當時我隻狗仔又係由細陪到我大<br />\n係診所度喊到崩潰"},{"pid":"95c5a9843043e9e5d9169df8211d3e46264cd7ea","tid":339833,"uid":91362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果狗狗走之前係好多病痛嘅<br />\n而家對佢黎講係一個解脫<br />\n明白你會好難過<br />\n愛狗嘅人真係會當狗仔係自己嘅家人<br />\n而家可以做嘅就係平復心情<br />\n將你對佢嘅愛擺落其他動物到<br />\n有能力嘅就再領養多幾隻<br />\n驚再一次傷痛唔敢養嘅話就多啲去做動物義工 照顧其他動物<br />\n相信你隻狗仔都希望你會將對佢嘅愛攞黎幫助其他狗仔<br />\n佢而家應該會過左彩虹橋去同其他狗仔一齊好開心咁玩 你唔使擔心佢 佢都會掛住你嘅"},{"pid":"feffefbb34b6b5d8c01fdb5925170aae4371a6bf","tid":339833,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"7ba332dcb4e15662a9e17daccd659cba661b1b1d","tid":339833,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時我隻狗仔又係由細陪到我大<br />\n係診所度喊到崩潰</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bdb311c04f9aee60262fb1b6e4c5d60e31c263","tid":339833,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"我嗰隻都係無幾耐之前走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be9afe0ac02c5ea689829d4a5e4c66d61a3a10e","tid":339833,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"冇,喊夠,你個人會自然收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb0b7d3142df36f0a7c731c10d3c5dfa640661a","tid":339833,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:55:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果狗狗走之前係好多病痛嘅<br />\n而家對佢黎講係一個解脫<br />\n明白你會好難過<br />\n愛狗嘅人真係會當狗仔係自己嘅家人<br />\n而家可以做嘅就係平復心情<br />\n將你對佢嘅愛擺落其他動物到<br />\n有能力嘅就再領養多幾隻<br />\n驚再一次傷痛唔敢養嘅話就多啲去做動物義工 照顧其他動物<br />\n相信你隻狗仔都希望你會將對佢嘅愛攞黎幫助其他狗仔<br />\n佢而家應該會過左彩虹橋去同其他狗仔一齊好開心咁玩 你唔使擔心佢 佢都會掛住你嘅</blockquote><br />\n我諗我未必可以咁快養過第二隻，始終陪左我好多年，唔會代替到我對佢既感情，btw 多謝巴打既建議"},{"pid":"e1d4a90c0d4ddd13e790e9d82f3559d1ec54f2a0","tid":339833,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707c6917786d39e558fd2bb9838c276854e8a6f3","tid":339833,"uid":132055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好太傷心巴打<br />\n我自己都擔心緊隻老狗<br />\n成10幾歲日日喺度顛顛得得 會唔會突然有一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 唯有諗開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0415a90c6532a245de1fc17fbf1885c16ba3b5e6","tid":339833,"uid":3846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:57:01.000Z","msg":"巴打振作<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d730189c743ad1ec55fa65c85be87fb34de24d83","tid":339833,"uid":31859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"你養咗八年 我養咗十七年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢細我一歲真係由細睇到我大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a85e7b9303df4f14ecef475427ddf042b05516","tid":339833,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇,喊夠,你個人會自然收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩既，但當我返到屋企，突然少左D吠叫聲，真係忍唔住流幾滴眼淚"},{"pid":"d02f6a3537a7f3126a422cfd51d1f94e5f85ad41","tid":339833,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:00:30.000Z","msg":"俾你照顧一生一世已是狗狗的福氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6623b6ccefdadfcad9e6bbcba6f8da7ea1fc0b0d","tid":339833,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好太傷心巴打<br />\n我自己都擔心緊隻老狗<br />\n成10幾歲日日喺度顛顛得得 會唔會突然有一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 唯有諗開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打真係要好好對佢啊"},{"pid":"03ad02052cd0daccd26ca1215caceea9b72c4860","tid":339833,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇,喊夠,你個人會自然收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩既，但當我返到屋企，突然少左D吠叫聲，真係忍唔住流幾滴眼淚</blockquote><br />\n我一開門見到張sofa少左d野就跪左係度喊,而家講起都眼濕濕,頭幾日我晚晚坐係sofa望住佢個私家位喊"},{"pid":"dc83be2161548bc1c64d5a395185014a653911be","tid":339833,"uid":1870,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾你照顧一生一世已是狗狗的福氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時候我覺得人同動物既感情比起人與人之間更加深厚，雖然唔能夠同佢溝通，但正正因為咁，有d心底裡既說話只會同佢講，然後佢會向你撒撒嬌，好似安慰你咁，呢種無聲既互動係冇一個人可以比到我，調返轉講應該係佢照顧我"},{"pid":"a324ffa669c433c715c68fedef8a09de14a44334","tid":339833,"uid":3685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e07c11b05bf0b06982912ea491cd3ba7180aa4","tid":339833,"uid":1870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你養咗八年 我養咗十七年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢細我一歲真係由細睇到我大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十七年...代入返人類應該80幾歲.."},{"pid":"cf007732019d57e39fe38b92681e17957b0c7378","tid":339833,"uid":47147,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db53f2b4772e91b35d24d2e40762313b9d2d8c66","tid":339833,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你養咗八年 我養咗十七年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢細我一歲真係由細睇到我大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十七年...代入返人類應該80幾歲..</blockquote><br />\n我以前o個隻都係17-8歲,<br />\n睇醫生話有好大粒腫瘤,醫生話康復機會低,年紀又老,打針減低佢痛苦重好。<br />\n老母應承左但我好唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578625d084485e9fc8a9d6d053af027ac15a4a6e","tid":339833,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:48:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20ee02d10a950b0b216bae6b397f831c96879c91","tid":339833,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/05/041213_86fafd897aa09097d275a6bd406d50e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F05%2F041213_86fafd897aa09097d275a6bd406d50e2.jpg&h=b3b376d1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}